es that face our customers with gamechanging ground maritime space and intelligence cyber satellite communication products and missionrelated capabilities the company has more than  locations worldwide and employs more than  employees as president of general dynamics c systems mr marzilli led the company to global prominence as a trusted provider of tactical and public safety command control communications intelligence surveillance and reconnaissance products and systems used by the us army and government agencies worldwide mr marzilli earned a bachelor’s degree from middlebury college graduating with honors as a dana scholar he joined gte in  which was later acquired by general dynamics in  he proudly sits on several charitable boards with one in particular the sentinels of freedom scholarship foundation serving the needs of the most severely wounded post veterans you can follow chris on twitter at gdmspresident click here to download chris marzillis bio pdf                      about us our mission how we work open architecture user experience meet our ux team ux image gallery edge innovation sourcing network environmental health  safety innovation international general dynamics mission systemscanada general dynamics united kingdom limited mediaware page europa leadership team community investment behind the scenes recent news general dynamics delivers 0th air traffic control radio to federal aviation administration and us department of defense in the news soldiers evaluate wint’s tcnlite for nie  austal usa austal usa celebrates christening of usns city of bismarck epf  social media connect with gd mission systems on social media contact us                  × tell us about yourself we would like to learn more about you so we can better serve you your privacy is important to us learn more about our privacy policy nameemailphoneorganizationtitlemessage close × tell us about yourself we would like to learn more about you so we can better serve you your privacy is im